Coordinated Advertising Technology

Our AI-powered technology enables advertisers to create a= ds that resemble the wardrobes of popular YouTubers. By analyzing their fas= hion choices, our system generates visually similar ads that resonate with = the target audience.

An AI-powered fashion style recommendation solution that reflects natio= nal trends.
Id= entified limitations of existing AI style recommendation solutions in the m= arket through collaboration with Korean fashion companies and academia. The= problem was the confirmation bias of AI models (data pattern learning), wh= ich prevented the recommendation of trendy styles. This issue was resolved = using a self-developed AI and has been patented.

Coordinated Adve= rtising Technology Our AI-powered technology enables advertisers to create = ads that resemble the wardrobes of popular YouTubers. By analyzing their fa= shion choices, our system generates visually similar ads that resonate with= the target audience.
Benefits for Google Increase in Exposure By adopting the coordinated= advertising technology, Google can attract more users and expand its reach= , resulting in higher ad impressions. The visually appealing nature of the = ads will capture users' attention, leading to a higher number of clicks on = Google's platform. With ads resembling popular YouTubers' outfits, users wi= ll be more inclined to click on these ads, resulting in an improved click-t= hrough rate. The engaging and relatable nature of the ads will drive higher= conversion rates, ensuring a better return on investment for advertisers o= n Google. By offering visually appealing coordinated ads, Google can delive= r higher-quality leads to advertisers, resulting in a better return on adve= rtising spend for both parties. Increase in Clicks Improved CVR Higher CTR = Better ROAS

  1. Influencer Partnerships= Google can collaborate with popular YouTubers to showcase their coordinate= d ads in their videos, leveraging their influence and expanding the reach t= o their dedicated audience.
  1. Targeted Ad Segments T= hrough our coordinated advertising technology, Google can create specific a= d segments that cater to different fashion styles and preferences, capturin= g users' attention with personalized content.
  1. Ana= lytics & Optimization We offer advanced analytics and optimization tool= s that allow advertisers to track the performance of coordinated ads, enabl= ing Google to enhance their advertising platform with data-driven insights.=
Mutual Benefits = 1 User Engagement Users will enjoy seeing ads that align with their interes= ts and style preferences, leading to increased engagement and a positive us= er experience on Google's platform. 2 Innovative Advertising With coordinat= ed ads, Google can stay at the forefront of advertising innovation, attract= ing more advertisers and maintaining a competitive edge in the market. 3 Re= venue Growth By providing advertisers with effective advertising solutions,= Google can generate increased revenue through higher ad spend and improved= ROI for advertisers.
Predicted Collaboration Returns Based on market analysis and previou= s successes, we predict a significant increase in ad revenue for Google, wi= th a projected growth of 20% in the first year of implementing the coordina= ted advertising technology.
